  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK265">
<l>vēṇṭiya vēṇṭiyāṅ keytalāṟ ceytava</l>
<l>mīṇṭu muyalap paṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Religious dislipline is practised in this world, because it secures the attainment of whatever one may wish to enjoy (in the world to come).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
